Initialize Terraform
    command:terraform init
    Purpose:Initializes Terraform working directory

2.Validate Configuration
    command:terraform validate
    Purpose:Checks Terraform syntax and configuration validity

3.Format Terraform Files
    command:terraform fmt
    Purpose:Formats Terraform code properly

4.Generate Execution Plan
    command:terraform plan
    Purpose:Shows infrastructure changes before applying

5.Apply Infrastructure
    commandterraform apply
    Purpose:Creates or updates infrastructure resources

6.Destroy Infrastructure
    command:terraform destroy
    Purpose:Deletes infrastructure managed by Terraform

7.Show Terraform State
    command:terraform show
    Purpose:Displays Terraform state information

8.List Terraform Resources
    command:terraform state list
    Purpose:Shows resources managed by Terraform